Request Validation:
- Verify requester and department
- Confirm manager approval is attached
- Review business justification
- Check budget allocation/cost center

Equipment Specification:
- Determine equipment type needed
- Identify user's role and requirements
- Select appropriate model per standards
- Note any special requirements (high performance, portability)

{% if equipment_type == 'laptop' %}
Laptop Request:
- Select laptop model based on role (standard, power user, developer)
- Determine RAM and storage requirements
- Check for specific GPU needs if applicable
- Verify docking station compatibility
- Include carrying case if mobile worker
{% endif %}

{% if equipment_type == 'monitor' %}
Monitor Request:
- Determine size requirement (24", 27", 32")
- Check for dual monitor needs
- Verify resolution requirements
- Confirm mounting needs (stand, arm)
- Check port compatibility with user's laptop
{% endif %}

{% if equipment_type == 'peripheral' %}
Peripheral Request:
- Identify specific peripheral needed
- Verify compatibility with user's setup
- Check wireless vs wired preference
- Select from approved vendor list
{% endif %}

{% if equipment_type == 'docking_station' %}
Docking Station Request:
- Match dock to laptop model
- Verify port requirements (monitors, USB)
- Check power delivery requirements
- Include required cables
{% endif %}

Procurement Process:
- Check internal inventory for available stock
- Create purchase requisition if not in stock
- Obtain quotes from approved vendors
- Submit for procurement approval
- Track order status

Asset Preparation:
- Receive and inspect equipment
- Create asset record in inventory system
- Apply asset tag
- Image device with corporate build (if applicable)
- Install required software
- Configure for user

Deployment:
- Schedule delivery or pickup with user
- Provide user with setup instructions
- Connect with user to verify functionality
- Document asset assignment to user

Post-Deployment:
- Update asset management records
- Close procurement tickets
- Send warranty information to user
- Schedule follow-up if needed
